==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Meaking
<hw>Meak"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Meak</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>The process of picking out the oakum from the
seams of a vessel which is to be recalked.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Meaking iron</b></col> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>, <cd>the tool
with which old oakum is picked out of a vessel's seams.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Meal</ent>⟦br⟧
